==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sciatic
<hw>Sci*at"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>sciatique</ets>, LL. <ets>sciaticus</ets>, from L.
<ets>ischiadicus</ets>, Gr. <?/. See <er>Ischiadic</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the hip; in the region of,
or affecting, the hip; ischial; ischiatic; <as>as, the <ex>sciatic</ex>
nerve, <ex>sciatic</ex> pains</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sciatic</ent>⟦br⟧

